==English==
===Noun===
'''curry'''

# a mixture of [[spice]]s, usually including [[turmeric]], also known as ''[[curry powder]]''.
# a sauce whose main component is curry powder.
# an Asian-style [[dish]] or [[stew]] made with curry.

